      <title>北方信托季度利润因资产管理费用增加而增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/northern-trust-quarterly-profit-jumps-higher-fee-asset-management-2024-10-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北方信托周三公布第三季度利润增长 42%，得益于服务和管理客户资产的费用收入增加，推动该资产和财富管理公司的股价在盘前交易中上涨 4.4%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/northern-trust-quarterly-profit-jumps-higher-fee-asset-management-2024-10-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 12:16:46 GMT</pubDate>
