      <title>意大利银行业游说领袖认为定期存款竞争日趋激烈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-banking-lobby-chief-sees-rising-competition-term-deposits-2024-10-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利银行业协会 (ABI) 主席周三表示，由于欧洲央行不断减少债券购买量，从金融系统抽走现金，银行将不得不更加激烈地竞争以获得中长期资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-banking-lobby-chief-sees-rising-competition-term-deposits-2024-10-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 23 Oct 2024 11:20:05 GMT</pubDate>
